  "response": "Pondicherry, also known as Puducherry, is home to several software and IT companies. Some of the notable ones include:\n\n1. **Syncfusion** - Known for providing software components and tools widely used in web and mobile development.\n2. **Invence Technologies** - Offers software development, web development, and various IT solutions.\n3. **Brainguru Technologies** - Focuses on digital marketing, web development, and SEO services.\n4. **CG-VAK** - Provides software development services and IT staffing solutions.\n5. **Avria Technologies Pvt Ltd** - Specializes in web and mobile app development alongside custom software solutions.\n6. **Yalamanchili Software** - Develops payment systems and banking technology.\n\nThese companies highlight the growing presence of IT services and software development in Pondicherry. If you are looking for a specific service or niche, it's recommended to directly contact these firms to discuss your requirements.",
